    "Details of used metrics for different tasks are shown in Table 1.",
    "However, matching-based metrics are not specialized for evaluating the usefulness of the LLMs in clinical practice.",
    "To assist clinicians, it is necessary to provide faithful, comprehensive, and robust content (Thirunavukarasu et al., 2023; Arora and Arora, 2023; Safranek et al., 2023).",
    "Faithfulness LLMs are susceptible to \"hallucinations\" (Li et al., 2023a; Ji et al., 2023), i.e., fluent content that appears credible but factually incorrect or potentially harmful.",
    "Therefore, it is crucial to ensure that LLMs generate faithful content, so that the models do not generate contents that \"do not exist\" according to clinicians (Liu et al., 2022)."
